trans-unit.source: A base class for <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ObjectItemCollection"></xref>, <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.EdmItemCollection"></xref>, and <xref href="System.Data.Mapping.StorageMappingItemCollection"></xref> classes.

trans-unit.source: An ItemCollection class is an abstract class and provides the core API for loading and holding the in-memory metadata.
trans-unit.target: ItemCollection 類別是抽象類別，並提供核心 API 來載入和保存記憶體中中繼資料。

trans-unit.source: This class is derived from the <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReadOnlyMetadataCollection%601> class.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別衍生自<xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReadOnlyMetadataCollection%601>類別。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Item Collections (Metadata)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/3051a40a-ff45-42f8-8f93-7545e427a404).
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱[項目集合 （中繼資料）](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/3051a40a-ff45-42f8-8f93-7545e427a404)。
